I promise to always stand by your side and honour you 
I am so excited to be your wife not only today but for the rest of our lives and share the journey of life with you and Rio as a family.
525,600 minutes a year 525,600 moments to be the best versions of ourselves for one another
I vow to support you to inspire you to show you how to be a superior man for me and therefore for the world. 
Because when you shine the world shines. 
When you’re overflowing you have so much to pour out onto the world. 
So I vow to always praise you, always touch you and you adore, always raise you up, always give you a Grammy when introducing you on club house 😉 
To always be addicted to one another, to listen to you to respect you. 
To be the best mother to our children. 
To be a phenomenal wife to you forever more. 

Michael, thank you for your love. I thank God every day for bringing me to you ♥️🙏🏼

GUYS IT'S TIME! 

Link in Bio for my INSANE chat with @tombilyeu Entrepreneur & Founder of @impacttheory ! 
On this episode of the podcast, you’ll learn about: 

✅Tom's BILLION DOLLAR EXIT  from Quest 

✅The need to redefine how people see success as an Entrepreneur 

✅ The "Learner" Mindset and how to shift into a Learner's reality
 
✅How Being your most Authentic self is the Key to Success 

✅The Human Biological Experience and how we can control our Biochemical Cocktail 

This is THE podcast that can change your life! When you listen to a podcast or read a book, for the duration of that time you are listening to that expert or author you are literally being 1:1 mentored by them!! You are getting into their thought process and understanding how to better your life through their teachings. It is priceless!!

I AM so THANKFUL for all of the ratings & reviews that have been pouring in! Those ratings & reviews are the way that this show grows, and it’s because of you that I can keep putting out these amazing interviews!

✨✨✨

node.text:
Don’t you just love children’s excitement and creative imaginations?! From being a single mom for so many years it taught me how to open my mind up to the pursuit of fun and happiness. Every day when I ask my son, what do you want to do today? he replies with; I want to play and have fun in the playground! This same excitement they have for the playground and play is the same excitement we as adults should have for life and all of life’s treasures. If we woke up every day seeking joy and excitement we would in turn receive situations, events and people into our life that match those feelings. Instead of letting the work or a stressful situation rule your life and dictate your day, wake up and seek activities, events and people that make you live from a place of your highest inspiration and excitement. 
.
Thank you for such a beautiful stay @hotelkensington for Rio’s birthday ♥️
